name: DEKIBAE
tagline: できばえ【出来栄え・出来映え】① でき上がりの具合。「―がいい」 ② でき上がりのすぐれていること。「意外なる―にて」〈当世書生気質逍遥〉
body:
### Why do we do THIS?
This is a research project. The idea came from the awkward moments prevalent to a routine frontend dev, with jQuery, jQuery plugins and JavaScript frameworks in her toolbox - 

```
Occasionally, the external code behaves JUST NOT AS EXPECTED.
```
